ts.html\" data-sqsp-block=\"text\" data-website-component-id=\"yui_3_17_2_1_1765174132487_2418\" id=\"block-yui_3_17_2_1_1765174132487_2418\"><div class=\"sqs-block-content\"><div class=\"sqs-text-block-container\">\n  \n  <div class=\"sqs-html-content\" data-sqsp-text-block-content><p style=\"text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;\" class=\"sqsrte-small\"><span class=\"sqsrte-text-color--custom\" style=\"color: #6A6360\">微物設計創辦人 Roger 盧紀帆&nbsp; / Photo Credit：盧紀帆</span></p><p class=\"\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">走進微物設計的接待空間，第一眼會誤以為踏入了一間藝廊。精挑細選的藝術收藏、軟裝色彩層層疊疊，卻又意外和諧。這裡就像是總監盧紀帆（以下稱 Roger）的縮影——如藝術家一般的敏銳，如工匠一般執著。空間裡瀰漫著低調而沈穩的氣息，讓人瞬間靜下來，感受到他獨有的審美與態度。</p><p class=\"\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">對 Roger 而言，看似鮮明的風格背後，「我」永遠放在最後。來自藝術背景的他，把每一次專案都視作一段創作歷程，在功能與需求之間，耐心找出能與業主共鳴的答案。</p><p class=\"\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\"><br></p></div>\n\n\n  \n<style id=\"container-styles\">#block-yui_3_17_2_1_1765174132487_2418 {\n    \n    --stroke-style: none;--stroke-thickness: 6px;\n    \n      \n      \n      \n    \n\n--tweak-text-block-background-color: initial;\n\n  }\n\n  #block-yui_3_17_2_1_1765174132487_2418 .sqs-html-content {\n    \n    --tweak-text-block-padding: 6% 6% 6% 6%;\n  --tweak-text-block-padding: initial;\n}\n\n  #block-yui_3_17_2_1_1765174132487_2418 {\n      mix-blend-mode: var(--tweak-text-block-blend\n  );\n      border-radius: var(--tweak-text-block-radius);\n  }\n\n  \n  \n#block-yui_3_17_2_1_1765174132487_2418 {\n      --tweak-text-block-radius: 0px 0px 0px 0px;\n    }\n\n\n  \n  \n\n  #block-yui_3_17_2_1_1765174132487_2418 {\n    }\n\n</style>\n\n<style id=\"override-container-styles\">\n    @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {\n          \n            \n\n#block-yui_3_17_2_1_1765174132487_2418 {\n            \n            }\n        }\n    \n  \n    @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {\n          #block-yui_3_17_2_1_1765174132487_2418 .sqs-html-content {\n            \n            }\n        }\n    \n  @media screen and (max-width: 767px) 