ata-loader=\"sqs\">\n\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        \n          \n        \n\n        \n      \n        </figure>\n      \n\n    </div>\n  \n\n\n  \n\n\n</div></div><div class=\"sqs-block website-component-block sqs-block-website-component sqs-block-html html-block\" data-block-css=\"[&quot;https://definitions.sqspcdn.com/website-component-definition/static-assets/website.components.html/d92a980d-b660-49d1-a8a9-d817239fa29e_741/website.components.html.styles.css&quot;]\" data-block-scripts=\"[&quot;https://definitions.sqspcdn.com/website-component-definition/static-assets/website.components.html/d92a980d-b660-49d1-a8a9-d817239fa29e_741/website.components.html.visitor.js&quot;]\" data-block-type=\"1337\" data-definition-name=\"website.components.html\" data-sqsp-block=\"text\" data-website-component-id=\"yui_3_17_2_1_1765174845243_4641\" id=\"block-yui_3_17_2_1_1765174845243_4641\"><div class=\"sqs-block-content\"><div class=\"sqs-text-block-container\">\n  \n  <div class=\"sqs-html-content\" data-sqsp-text-block-content><p style=\"text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;\" class=\"sqsrte-small\"><span class=\"sqsrte-text-color--custom\" style=\"color: #6A6360\">微物展間一角，木樁嵌入結構，由 Roger 親手刷上金漆，筆觸清晰可見</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;\" class=\"sqsrte-small\"><span class=\"sqsrte-text-color--custom\" style=\"color: #6A6360\">&nbsp;Photo Credit：盧紀帆</span></p><p class=\"\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">在美術學院求學的日子裡，Roger 養成了「追根究底」的習慣。從材料、脈絡、理念到創作背景，都必須能清楚論述，並在務實的基礎上提出個人觀點。他認為，專業的藝術家必須對媒材有十足的掌握，這是職人精神的追求——願意花二十年的時間去摸索一種材料的本質。</p><p class=\"\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">「這也是我覺得山恩很特別的地方，」Roger 分享，「從第一次參加 Salon 認識你們，就覺得你們能堅持材料知識和理念的推廣這麼久，是非常令人敬佩的。」</p></div>\n\n\n  \n<style id=\"container-styles\">#block-yui_3_17_2_1_1765174845243_4641 {\n    \n    --stroke-style: none;--stroke-thickness: 6px;\n    \n      \n      \n      \n    \n\n--tweak-text-block-background-color: initial;\n\n  }\n\n  #block-yui_3_17_2_1_1765174845243_4641 .sqs-html-content {\n    \n    --tweak-text-block-padding: 6% 6% 6% 6%;\n  --tweak-text-block-padding: initial;\n}\n\n  #block-yui_3_17_2_1_1765174845243_4641 {\n      mix-blend-mode: var(--tweak-text-block-blend\n  );\n      border-radius: var(--tweak-text-block-radius);\n  }\n\n  \n  \n#block-yui_3_17_2_1_1765174845243_4641 {\n      --tweak-text-block-radius: 0px 0px 0px 0px;\n    }\n\n\n  \n  \n\n  #block-yui_3_17_2_1_1765174845243_4641 {\n    }\n\n</style>\n\n<style id=\"override-container-styles\">\n    @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {\n          \n            \n\n#block-yui_3_17_2_1_1765174845243_4641 {\n            \n            }\n        }\n    \n  \n    @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {\n          #block-yui_3_17_2_1_1765174845243_4641 .sqs-html-content {\n            \n            }\n        }\n    \n  @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {\n          \n          \n\n          \n          \n          \n        }</style>\n\n<style class=\"transform-overrides-vars\">\n    \n  </style>\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div></div><div class=\"sqs-block image-block sqs-block-image\" data-block-type=\"5\" data-sqsp-block=\"image-classic\" id=\"block-yui_3_17_2_1_1765174845243_5944\"><div class=\"sqs-block-content\">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n    \n  \n    <div\n        class=\"\n          image-block-outer-wrapper\n          layout-caption-hidden\n          design-layout-inline\n          combination-animation-site-default\n          individual-animation-site-default\n          individual-text-animation-site-default\n        \"\n        data-test=\"image-block-inline-outer-wrapper\"\n        data-sqsp-image-classic-block-layout=\"inline\"\n    >\n\n      \n\n      \n        <figure\n            class=\"\n              sqs-block-image-figure\n              intrinsic\n            \"\n            style=\"max-width:3000px;\"\n        >\n          \n        \n        \n\n        \n          \n            \n  