n\n    </div>\n  \n\n\n  \n\n\n</div></div><div class=\"sqs-block website-component-block sqs-block-website-component sqs-block-html html-block\" data-block-css=\"[&quot;https://definitions.sqspcdn.com/website-component-definition/static-assets/website.components.html/d92a980d-b660-49d1-a8a9-d817239fa29e_741/website.components.html.styles.css&quot;]\" data-block-scripts=\"[&quot;https://definitions.sqspcdn.com/website-component-definition/static-assets/website.components.html/d92a980d-b660-49d1-a8a9-d817239fa29e_741/website.components.html.visitor.js&quot;]\" data-block-type=\"1337\" data-definition-name=\"website.components.html\" data-sqsp-block=\"text\" data-website-component-id=\"yui_3_17_2_1_1765174845243_6680\" id=\"block-yui_3_17_2_1_1765174845243_6680\"><div class=\"sqs-block-content\"><div class=\"sqs-text-block-container\">\n  \n  <div class=\"sqs-html-content\" data-sqsp-text-block-content><p style=\"text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;\" class=\"sqsrte-small\"><span class=\"sqsrte-text-color--custom\" style=\"color: #6A6360\">熱愛手作的 Roger，總喜歡親手與材料相處</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;\" class=\"sqsrte-small\"><span class=\"sqsrte-text-color--custom\" style=\"color: #6A6360\">Photo Credit：盧紀帆</span></p><p class=\"\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">「在眾多限制與需求條件下，很像回到創作過程，你今天有一張紙，可能不是最喜歡的手工紙，而是另一種紙或畫布。」Roger 表示設計師的的價值在於「把業主的理念、企業目標、創業精神，轉換成實體內容，出現在必要動線上，同時考慮落地的空間邏輯。」一路從創作到設計實踐，Roger 從未後悔走上一條看似不輕鬆的道路，「從圖紙到工地現場，墨線彈完、角料開始下去，你就知道你的設計正在落實，這是多棒的一件事！」Roger 眼中閃著光。</p></div>\n\n\n  \n<style id=\"container-styles\">#block-yui_3_17_2_1_1765174845243_6680 {\n    \n    --stroke-style: none;--stroke-thickness: 6px;\n    \n      \n      \n      \n    \n\n--tweak-text-block-background-color: initial;\n\n  }\n\n  #block-yui_3_17_2_1_1765174845243_6680 .sqs-html-content {\n    \n    --tweak-text-block-padding: 6% 6% 6% 6%;\n  --tweak-text-block-padding: initial;\n}\n\n  #block-yui_3_17_2_1_1765174845243_6680 {\n      mix-blend-mode: var(--tweak-text-block-blend\n  );\n      border-radius: var(--tweak-text-block-radius);\n  }\n\n  \n  \n#block-yui_3_17_2_1_1765174845243_6680 {\n      --tweak-text-block-radius: 0px 0px 0px 0px;\n    }\n\n\n  \n  \n\n  #block-yui_3_17_2_1_1765174845243_6680 {\n    }\n\n</style>\n\n<style id=\"override-container-styles\">\n    @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {\n          \n            \n\n#block-yui_3_17_2_1_1765174845243_6680 {\n            \n            }\n        }\n    \n  \n    @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {\n          #block-yui_3_17_2_1_1765174845243_6680 .sqs-html-content {\n            \n            }\n        }\n    \n  @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {\n          \n          \n\n          \n          \n          \n        }</style>\n\n<style class=\"transform-overrides-vars\">\n    \n  </style>\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div></div><div class=\"sqs-block image-block sqs-block-image\" data-block-type=\"5\" data-sqsp-block=\"image-classic\" id=\"block-yui_3_17_2_1_1765174845243_7974\"><div class=\"sqs-block-content\">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n    \n  \n    <div\n        class=\"\n          image-block-outer-wrapper\n          layout-caption-hidden\n          design-layout-inline\n          combination-animation-site-default\n          individual-animation-site-default\n          individual-text-animation-site-default\n        \"\n        data-test=\"image-block-inline-outer-wrapper\"\n        data-sqsp-image-classic-block-layout=\"inline\"\n    >\n\n      \n\n      \n        <figure\n            class=\"\n              sqs-block-image-figure\n              intrinsic\n            \"\n            style=\"max-width:3000px;\"\n        >\n          \n        \n        \n\n        \n          \n            \n          <div\n              \n              \n              class=\"image-block-wrapper\"\n              data-animation-role=\"image\"\n              \n  \n\n          >\n            <div data-sqsp-image-classic-block-image-container class=\"sqs-image-shape-container-element\n              \n          \n        \n              has-aspect-ratio\n            \" style=\"\n                position: relative;\n                \n                  padding-bottom:66.66667175292969%;\n                \n                overflow: hidden;-webkit-mask-image: -webkit-radial-gradient(white, black);\n              \"\n              >\n                \n                \n                \n                \n                \n                \n                \n                <img data-stretch=\"false\" data-src=\"/images/c02987de-c372-4cd0-bd7c-d81e251a92f7/_13.jpg\" data-image=\"/images/c02987de-c372-4cd0-bd7c-d81e251a92f7/_13.jpg\" data-image-dimensions=\"3000x2000\" data-image-focal-point=\"0.5,0.5\" alt=\"\" data-load=\"false\" elementtiming=\"system-image-block\" data-sqsp-image-classic-block-image src=\"/images/c02987de-c372-4cd0-bd7c-d81e251a92f7/_13.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\" alt=\"\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, (max-width: 767px) 100vw, 100vw\" style=\"display:block;object-fit: cover; width: 100%; height: 100%; object-position: 50% 50%\" onload=\"this.classList.add(&quot;loaded&quot;)\" srcset=\"/images/c02987de-c372-4cd0-bd7c-d81e251a92f7/_13.jpg 100w, /images/c02987de-c372-4cd0-bd7c-d81e251a92f7/_13.jpg 300w, /images/c02987de-c372-4cd0-bd7c-d81e251a92f7/_13.jpg 500w, /images/c02987de-c372-4cd0-bd7c-d81e251a92f7/_13.jpg 750w, /images/c02987de-c372-4cd0-bd7c-d81e251a92f7/_13.jpg 1000w, /images/c02987de-c372-4cd0-bd7c-d81e251a92f7/_13.jpg 1500w, /images/c02987de-c372-4cd0-bd7c-d81e251a92f7/_13.jpg 2500w\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-loader=\"sqs\">\n\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        \n          \n        \n\n        \n      \n        </figure>\n      \n\n    </div>\n  \n\n\n  \n\n\n</div></div><div class=\"sqs-block website-component-block sqs-block-website-component sqs-block-html html-block\" data-block-css=\"[&quot;https://definitions.sqspcdn.com/website-component-definition/static-assets/website.components.html/d92a980d-b660-49d1-a8a9-d817239fa29e_741/website.components.html.styles.css&quot;]\" data-block-scripts=\"[&quot;https://definitions.sqspcdn.com/website-component-definition/static-assets/website.components.html/d92a980d-b660-49d1-a8a9-d817239fa29e_741/website.components.html.visitor.js&quot;]\" data-block-type=\"1337\" data-definition-name=\"website.components.html\" data-sqsp-block=\"text\" data-website-component-id=\"yui_3_17_2_1_1765174845243_8972\" id=\"block-yui_3_17_2_1_1765174845243_8972\"><div class=\"sqs-block-content\"><div class=\"sqs-text-block-container\">\n  \n  <div class=\"sqs-html-content\" data-sqsp-text-block-content><p style=\"text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;\" class=\"sqsrte-small\"><span class=\"sqsrte-text-color--custom\" style=\"color: #6A6360\">在眾多收藏品中，Roger 提到這幅《水花與彩虹》。<br> 「這幅畫像在繽紛燦爛的戰場上馳騁，雖然千瘡百孔、歷經風雨，卻正好象徵我的狀態，提醒我為什麼要堅持下去。」</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;\" class=\"sqsrte-small\"><span class=\"sqsrte-text-color--custom\" style=\"color: #6A6360\">Photo Credit：盧紀帆</span></p></div>\n\n\n  \n<style id=\"container-styles\">#block-yui_3_17_2_1_1765174845243_8972 {\n    \n    --stroke-style: none;--stroke-thickness: 6px;\n    \n      \n      \n      \n    \n\n--tweak-text-block-background-color: initial;\n\n  }\n\n  #block-yui_3_17_2_1_1765174845243_8972 .sqs-html-content {\n    \n    --tweak-text-block-padding: 6% 6% 6% 6%;\n  --tweak-text-block-padding: initial;\n}\n\n  #block-yui_3_17_2_1_1765174845243_8972 {\n      mix-blend-mode: var(--tweak-text-block-blend\n  );\n      border-radius: var(--tweak-text-block-radius);\n  }\n\n  \n  \n#block-yui_3_17_2_1_1765174845243_8972 {\n      --tweak-text-block-radius: 0px 0px 0px 0px;\n    }\n\n\n  \n  \n\n  #block-yui_3_17_2_1_1765174845243_8972 {\n    }\n\n</style>\n\n<style id=\"override-container-styles\">\n    @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {\n          \n            \n\n#block-yui_3_17_2_1_1765174845243_8972 {\n            \n            }\n        }\n    \n  \n    @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {\n          #block-yui_3_17_2_1_1765174845243_8972 .sqs-html-content {\n            \n            }\n        }\n    \n  @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {\n          \n          \n\n          \n          \n          \n        }</style>\n\n<style class=\"transform-overrides-vars\">\n    \n  </style>\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div></div><div class=\"sqs-block website-component-block sqs-block-website-component sqs-block-html html-block\" data-block-css=\"[&quot;https://definitions.sqspcdn.com/website-component-definition/static-assets/website.components.html/d92a980d-b660-49d1-a8a9-d817239fa29e_741/website.components.html.styles.css&quot;]\" data-block-scripts=\"[&quot;https://definitions.sqspcdn.com/website-component-definition/static-assets/website.components.html/d92a980d-b660-49d1-a8a9-d817239fa29e_741/website.components.html.visitor.js&quot;]\" data-block-type=\"1337\" data-definition-name=\"website.components.html\" data-sqsp-block=\"text\" data-website-component-id=\"yui_3_17_2_1_1765174845243_9584\" id=\"block-yui_3_17_2_1_1765174845243_9584\"><div class=\"sqs-block-content\"><div class=\"sqs-text-block-container\">\n  \n  <div class=\"sqs-html-content\" data-sqsp-text-block-content><p class=\"\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">微物設計走過第一個十年，Roger 這樣總結：「我想讓我們做的許多實驗、正在走的路都能看見成果，因為這正是微物成為今天的樣貌最可貴的養分。」對他而言，空間與專案之外，更重要的是營造一個健康的公司環境與文化——「現在我更看重微物的形象、做事的方法，以及價值觀。希望打造一個讓人安心的環境，當同事遇到困境或負面情緒時，公司能成為支撐他們的力量，讓大家願意在這裡成長、實現價值。」</p><p class=\"\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">他期許微物設計在日復一日的旅程中，持續在內省與自我認同之間，落實信念，並看見更多可能性。這，正是微物設計始終相信的哲學——<strong>「相信一切皆有可能」。</strong></p></div>\n\n\n  \n<style id=\"container-styles\">#block-yui_3_17_2_1_1765174845243_9584 {\n    \n    --stroke-style: none;--stroke-thickness: 6px;\n    \n      \n      \n      \n    \n\n--tweak-text-block-background-color: initial;\n\n  }\n\n  #block-yui_3_17_2_1_1765174845243_9584 .sqs-html-content {\n    \n    --tweak-text-block-padding: 6% 6% 6% 6%;\n  --tweak-text-block-padding: initial;\n}\n\n  #block-yui_3_17_2_1_1765174845243_9584 {\n      mix-blend-mode: var(--tweak-text-block-blend\n  );\n      border-radius: var(--tweak-text-block-radius);\n  }\n\n  \n  \n#block-yui_3_17_2_1_1765174845243_9584 {\n      --tweak-text-block-radius: 0px 0px 0px 0px;\n    }\n\n\n  \n  \n\n  #block-yui_3_17_2_1_1765174845243_9584 {\n    }\n\n</style>\n\n<style id=\"override-container-styles\">\n    @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {\n          \n            \n\n#block-yui_3_17_2_1_1765174845243_9584 {\n            \n            }\n        }\n    \n  \n    @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {\n          #block-yui_3_17_2_1_1765174845243_9584 .sqs-html-content {\n            \n            }\n        }\n    \n  @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {\n          \n          \n\n          \n          \n          \n        }</style>\n\n<style class=\"transform-overrides-vars\">\n    \n  </style>\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div></div></div></div></div>"
}